title: SCHC Makes Bullish Cross Above Critical Moving Average - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Thursday, shares of the SCHC ETF (Symbol: SCHC) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $31.71, changing hands as high as $31.76 per share.
